{"tid":1118360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我老豆成日偷食","createTime":"2019-04-21T11:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T17:25:35.000Z","uid":198204,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3db3d364a94d3240d9536558100880f42a9568e9","tid":1118360,"uid":198204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:06:59.000Z","msg":"CLS 喂大佬 都唔係第一次啦<br />\n成日襯我唔係屋企偷食我買個啲野食都算啦 ，食完又唔同我講，仲要求其擺埋一邊，唔搵保鮮紙保鮮袋之類入住，我點知有冇曱甴嗰啲走過入去。<br />\n我係屋企都仲好啲，會問我可唔可以食，我唔係屋企佢就問都唔會問，打個電話黎問可唔可以食有幾難？ <br />\n重點係仲要唔知錯喎，唔會話唔好意思/對唔住 食咗你啲野...<br />\n淨係識話最多買返幾包俾你 <br />\n有冇諗過唔係錢嘅問題 係尊重  <br />\n應該點樣串返佢 <br />\n我又唔會衰到落藥係啲野食到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBhyZis.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBhyZis.png&h=b16474c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52c312467bc8415d2687715e7c8c9f9dec2f90c3","tid":1118360,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:08:15.000Z","msg":"男人老狗咁小器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b30c78d687e5e69ec20e9229c1c977a9b39937","tid":1118360,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"攞夾萬鎖住啲嘢食"},{"pid":"633f92b556ab81ecfecc096a27f918f8ffd43748","tid":1118360,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:09:30.000Z","msg":"咁佢有冇真係買返比你先"},{"pid":"cdfabffaec463c16b051fced2632fe1e5eac9946","tid":1118360,"uid":140856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:11:49.000Z","msg":"你老母知唔知"},{"pid":"dad3e847102cc98b9af2e46a0972e5fda208e5d0","tid":1118360,"uid":198204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"633f92b556ab81ecfecc096a27f918f8ffd43748","tid":1118360,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:09:30.000Z","msg":"咁佢有冇真係買返比你先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"1cf05c66c9412983f61f68d311e769e6970667f8","tid":1118360,"uid":1760